'''2013年西亞-北非寒流'''是發生於2013年12月的{{link-en|冬季暴風雪|winter storm}}，它襲擊了[[中東地區|中東地區]]等地<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.skynews.com.au/world/article.aspx?id=933726|title=Winter storm pummels Middle East|date=2013-12-13|publisher=Sky News Australia|accessdate=2013-12-14|archive-date=2020-08-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200801022717/https://www.skynews.com.au/world/article.aspx?id=933726|dead-url=no}}</ref>。此次暴風雪被命名為「Alexa」，它已造成區域內數百萬貧困民眾與流離失所者受災，特別是[[敘利亞內戰|敘利亞內戰]]的難民群<ref name="YNewsI">{{cite web|url=http://news.yahoo.com/winter-storm-39-alexa-39-chills-middle-east-131856137.html|title=Wintry storm grips Middle East, worsens misery of Syrians|date=2013-12-13|publisher=Yahoo News|accessdate=2013-12-14|archive-date=2020-09-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200906183315/https://news.yahoo.com/winter-storm-39-alexa-39-chills-middle-east-131856137.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.voanews.com/content/reu-winter-storm-alexa-chills-the-middle-east/1809588.html|title=Winter Storm 'Alexa' Chills Middle East|date=2013-12-13|publisher=Voice of America|access-date=2013-12-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140105120829/http://www.voanews.com/content/reu-winter-storm-alexa-chills-the-middle-east/1809588.html|archive-date=2014-01-05|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。[[埃及|埃及]]首都[[開羅|開羅]]則在12月13日出現降雪，當地媒體宣稱此為112年以來首次。當地夜晚氣溫也降至2°C / 36°F<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.dailystar.com.lb/News/Middle-East/2013/Dec-13/240969-cairo-sees-first-snow-in-years-as-cold-snap-hits-egypt.ashx#axzz2nMzCNzyf|title=Cairo sees first snow in years as cold snap hits Egypt|date=2013-12-13|publisher=The Daily Star|accessdate=2013-12-14|archive-date=2019-05-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190503071911/http://www.dailystar.com.lb//News/Middle-East/2013/Dec-13/240969-cairo-sees-first-snow-in-years-as-cold-snap-hits-egypt.ashx#axzz2nMzCNzyf|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.huffingtonpost.co.uk/2013/12/13/snow-egypt-middle-east_n_4438571.html?utm_hp_ref=uk|title=Snow In Egypt For The First Time In 100 Years, Reports Say (PICTURES)|date=2013-12-13|publisher=The Huffington Post|accessdate=2013-12-14|archive-date=2018-02-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180216031035/http://www.huffingtonpost.co.uk/2013/12/13/snow-egypt-middle-east_n_4438571.html?utm_hp_ref=uk|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://english.ahram.org.eg/NewsContentP/1/89025/Egypt/Winter-brings-snow-to-Cairo.aspx|title=Winter brings snow to Cairo|date=2013-12-13|publisher=Ahram Online|accessdate=2013-12-14|archive-date=2019-03-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190327090204/http://english.ahram.org.eg/NewsContentP/1/89025/Egypt/Winter-brings-snow-to-Cairo.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref>。此外，[[以色列|以色列]]的部分道路也被迫關閉，[[本-古里安國際機場|本-古里安國際機場]]則因為雲層過厚停止運作，也促使[[美國國務卿|美國國務卿]][[約翰·凱瑞|約翰·凱瑞]]縮短與[[巴勒斯坦總統|巴勒斯坦總統]][[馬哈茂德·阿巴斯|馬哈茂德·阿巴斯]]的會談，趕在機場關閉前離開以色列<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.latimes.com/world/worldnow/la-fg-wn-snow-israel-egypt-20131213,0,1691393.story#axzz2nNFf0fk8|title=Snow closes roads in Israel, is a source of wonder in Cairo|date=2013-12-13|publisher=[[洛杉磯時報|洛杉磯時報]]|accessdate=2013-12-14|archive-date=2013-12-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131213164124/http://www.latimes.com/world/worldnow/la-fg-wn-snow-israel-egypt-20131213,0,1691393.story#axzz2nNFf0fk8|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="YNewsI"/>。

